s other raw materials the clay and limestone are then prehomogenized a process which consists of combining various types of clay and limestone the mix is dried and then fed into a grinder which grinds the various materials in preparation for the kiln the raw materials are calcined or processed at a high temperature in a kiln to produce clinker clinker is the intermediate product used in the manufacture of cement its types of cement include gray ordinary portland cement white portland cement masonry or mortar oilwell cement and blended cementreadymix concrete is a combination of cement fine and coarse aggregates admixtures which control properties of the concrete including plasticity pumpability freezethaw resistance strength and setting time and water the types of readymix concrete the company offers include standard readymix concrete architectural and decorative concrete rapidsetting concrete fiberreinforced concrete fluidfill concrete rollercompacted concrete selfconsolidating concrete scc pervious concrete and antibacterial concretethe company is a supplier of aggregates primarily the crushed stone sand and gravel used in various forms of construction the companys customers use its aggregates for an array of applications as a component in the construction and maintenance of highways walkways parking lots airport runways and railways for drainage water filtration purification and erosion control as fill material for sand traps on golf courses beaches playing field surfaces horse racing tracks and related applications and to build bridges homes and schools it also offers complementary products to its clients for their construction needs which mainly include asphalt concrete block roof tiles architectural products pipe and other precast productsmexicothe companys cemex mexico sa de cv cemex mexico subsidiary is both a holding company for some of the companys operating companies in mexico and an operating company involved in the manufacturing and distribution of cement aggregates steel groundstone and other construction materials and cement byproducts in mexico cemex mexico indirectly is also the holding company for substantially all the companys international operations its tepeaca cement plant in puebla mexico has a production capacity of approximately  million tons of cement per year the company operates over  out of its approximately  cement plants and over cement distribution centers including seven marine terminals located throughout mexicounited statescemex inc is the main holding company of the companys operating subsidiaries in the united states the company has a cement manufacturing capacity of approximately  million tons per year in its operations in the united states including over  million tons in proportional interests through noncontrolling holdings the company operates a geographically diverse base of over  cement plants located in alabama california colorado florida georgia kentucky louisiana ohio pennsylvania tennessee and texas it operates over  readymix concrete plants located in the alabama arizona california florida georgia louisiana new mexico nevada oregon tennessee texas and washington and aggregates facilities in arizona california florida georgia new mexico nevada oregon texas and washingtonnorthern europethe companys business in northern europe which includes its operations in the united kingdom germany france and its rest of northern europe segment the cemex investments limited is a holding company of its operating subsidiaries in the united kingdom the company is a provider of building materials in the united kingdom with vertically integrated cement readymix concrete aggregates and asphalt operations it is also a provider of concrete and precast materials solutions such as concrete blocks concrete block paving flooring systems and sleepers for rail infrastructurecemex deutschland ag is the companys main subsidiary in germany the company is a provider of building materials in germany with vertically integrated cement readymix concrete and aggregates cemex france is a main subsidiary in france the company is a readymix concrete producer and an aggregates producer in france it distributes its materials by road and waterways its operations in the rest of northern europe consisted primarily of its operations in the czech republic poland and latvia scandinavia and finlandcemex polska sp zoo is a main subsidiary in poland the company provides building materials in poland serving the cement readymix concrete and aggregates markets it operates over two cement plants and one grinding mill in poland with a total installed cement capacity of approximately three million tons per yearcemex sia is the companys operating subsidiary in latvia it operates a cement plant in latvia with an installed cement capacity of over  million tons per year the company also operates over nine readymix concrete plants a mobile pugmill and approximately four aggregates quarries in latvia the company operates over  marine cement terminals in norway and sweden through cemex as a bulkcement importer in the nordic regionthe mediterraneanthe companys business in the mediterranean which includes its operations in the spain egypt and its rest of the mediterranean segment the companys operations in the rest of the mediterranean consisted primarily of its operations in the united arab emirates and israelcemex espana is a holding company for the companys international operations acc is the subsidiary in egypt the company operates a cement plant in egypt with an annual installed capacity of approximately  million tons this plant is located approximately  miles south of cairo and serves the upper nile region of egypt as well as cairo and the delta region its united arab emirates companies include cemex topmix llc and cemex supermix llc which are readymix manufacturing companies and cemex falcon llc which specializes in the trading and production of cement and slag cemex holdings israel ltd is the companys subsidiary in israelsouth america and the caribbeanthe companys business in south america and the caribbean which includes its operations in the colombia and rest of south america and the caribbean segment cemex latam is the holding company for the companys operations in brazil colombia costa rica guatemala nicaragua panama and el salvador cemex colombia is its subsidiary in colombia its operations in the rest of south america and the caribbean consisted primarily of its operations in costa rica the dominican republic jamaica nicaragua panama puerto rico and other countries in the caribbean guatemala and small readymix concrete operations in argentina cemex dominicana sa is its subsidiary in the dominican republic and is a cement producer in the country cemex latam holdings sa cemex latam has interest in cemento bayano its subsidiary in panama and a cement producer in the country cemex latam owns cemex nicaragua sa which is an operating subsidiary in nicaragua cemex de puerto rico inc is its subsidiary in puerto rico cemex latam owns cemex guatemala which is an operating subsidiary in guatemalaasiathe companys business in asia which includes its operations in the philippines and the rest of asia segment the companys operations in the rest of asia which consists primarily of its operations in thailand bangladesh and malaysiathe company competes with lafargeholcim sociedad cooperativa cruz azul ciments molins grupo cementos de chihuahua sab de cv buzziunicem heidelberg ash grove cement crh heidelberg mittal investments schwenk italcementi vicat italcementi colas bouygues eurovia vinci lafarge dyckerhoff miebach skanska assiut cement company egyptian cement company italcementi spa arabian la union titan ameriyah national sinai sinai white cement south valley nile valley el sewedy army cement aswan medcom misr beni suef al nahda and misr quena cement companies building materials industries co asec cement cementos argos antioquia and southwest region markets lafargeho